1. *Razlogom* za to je loša organizacija. (The reason for that is poor organization.)
2. Tražio je *razlog* za svoje postupke. (He searched for a reason for his actions.)
3. Ona je *razlogom* što je ovo mesto tako lepo. (She is the reason why this place is so beautiful.)
4. Bez *razloga* je otišao. (He left for no reason.)
5. Sada *razlozi* za to postaju jasniji. (Now the reasons for that are becoming clearer.)
6. To nema *razloga*. (There is no reason for that.)
7. Ovo je *razlogom* zašto smo se odlučili na ovaj potez. (This is the reason why we decided to take this step.)
8. *Razlozi* za njegovo ponašanje su nepoznati. (The reasons for his behavior are unknown.)
9. On je *razlog* zašto smo svi ovde. (He is the reason why we are all here.)
10. Njegova odluka nema *razloga*. (His decision has no reason.)